description:
Had a chance to catch up with the legend that is Branford Marsalis!!
 
We chatted about everything from catching taxis whilst black to playing standards, the difference between playing Giant Steps and really playing Giant Steps, Botany, The Green Book and why he's no longer interested in playing for the youth!... plus a whole lot more 

recorded for BBC Radio 3 JAZZ NOW 
#JazzNow
